transcripts:
The local record store is where I fell in love with music. Camden, London is where I learned to live for music. 
Since I was young I always loved drawing,  so even if I lose the chance to do this as a living I'll always keep drawing.
I enjoy finding the extraordinary and very ordinary moments.
I dance every chance I get.
You can tell me what you want about my life and how I live, but this little life is mine and how I live is up to me.
I'm not a super cool person, but I like to express myself through my style online.
My job is my passion, and what I've wanted to do since I was a child. in this way I have achieved my aim.
